OL,3,C'We can't go on like this': Protestors
OL,4,Cslam airline for flight disruption
OL,6,FMore than 200 people have gathered at
OL,7,FAlderney Airport to protest the state
OL,8,Fof Aurigny's air services to and from
OL,9,Fthe island.
OL,11,FThe group assembled on Sunday
OL,12,Fafternoon (22 March), after the
OL,13,Fairline announced disruption to
OL,14,Fflights serving lifeline routes to
OL,15,FGuernsey and Southampton.
OL,17,FAurigny is blaming staff sickness and
OL,18,Fa lack of crew at Skybus, which runs
OL,19,Fthe Twin Otter plane services - with
OL,20,Fissues expected between Saturday 21
OL,21,Fand Thursday 26 March.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
