PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774353808
OL,3,C'We can't go on like this': Protestors
OL,4,Cslam airline for flight disruption
OL,6,FAurigny has defended its record,
OL,7,Fpointing out that in January and
OL,8,FFebruary this year, just 1.7% of its
OL,9,Fflights were cancelled due to
OL,10,Ftechnical or personnel issues.
OL,12,FThe airline's Chief Executive Officer,
OL,13,FNico Bezuidenhout, spoke to protestors
OL,14,Fat the airport.
OL,16,FHe said: "I'd like to apologise to
OL,17,Fpassengers for any disruption they may
OL,18,Fhave experienced over the last couple
OL,19,Fof months.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
