FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774353808
OL,3,C'We can't go on like this': Protestors
OL,4,Cslam airline for flight disruption
OL,6,F"When we have weather events, there's
OL,7,Fnothing we can do about that - what we
OL,8,Fcan take ownership of is technical
OL,9,Freliability and staff shortages when
OL,10,Fthey occur.
OL,12,F"We only cancelled 20 flights in
OL,13,FJanuary and February this year due to
OL,14,Fnon-weather-related reasons."
OL,16,FAnger has been brewing after an 87-
OL,17,Fyear-old man waited more than 48 hours
OL,18,Ffor emergency transport to Guernsey
OL,19,Ffollowing a heart attack in Alderney.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
