CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774353808
OL,3,C'We can't go on like this': Protestors
OL,4,Cslam airline for flight disruption
OL,6,FA medevac flight to Guernsey was
OL,7,Frepeatedly postponed due to weather
OL,8,Fand operational issues, with a boat
OL,9,Feventually chartered so he could
OL,10,Freceive appropriate medical attention.
OL,12,FLast week, Jeannie Cameron, Chair of
OL,13,FAlderney's Policy and Finance
OL,14,FCommittee, told ITV News that the
OL,15,Fisland's residents had "lost
OL,16,Fconfidence" in Aurigny.
OL,18,FSince Aurigny retired its Dornier
OL,19,Fplanes in November, Alderney has been
OL,20,Fserved by just one Twin Otter aircraft
OL,21,Ffor all of the operator's flights.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
